# Brainstorm / superpowers docs are local-only

This repository **gitignores** [`docs/superpowers/`](file:///C:/github/futureproofds/docs/superpowers).

## Required behavior

- Write brainstorming **specs**, **plans**, and related superpowers working docs **only** under `docs/superpowers/` (e.g. `docs/superpowers/specs/`, `docs/superpowers/plans/`).
- **Do not** `git add` or commit those paths—they are excluded from version control by design.
- **Do not** duplicate specs/plans into tracked locations (e.g. `data-cleaning-agent/docs/`, `docs/` at repo root, or product `README` files) **unless the user explicitly asks** for a tracked copy.

## Rationale

The user keeps brainstorm and implementation-plan artifacts **local**; the repo should not carry them in history.
